Interface GekCache<K,V>

public interface GekCache<K,V>

      • get

        @Nullable
V get(K key,
                 java.util.function.Function<? super K,? extends V> loader)
        Returns value associating with given key from this cache. If there is no entry for given key or the value is expired, a new value will be created by given loader.

        This method will return null if and only if the existed value or created value itself is null.

        Parameters:
        key - given key
        loader - given loader
        Returns:
        value associating with given key from this cache, or created one

      • getWrapper

        @Nullable
@Nullable GekWrapper<V> getWrapper(K key)
        Returns wrapped value associating with given key from this cache, or null if there is no entry for given key or the value is expired.
        Parameters:
        key - given key
        Returns:
        value associating with given key from this cache

      • getWrapper

        @Nullable
@Nullable GekWrapper<V> getWrapper(K key,
                                              java.util.function.Function<? super K,GekWrapper<? extends V>> loader)
        Returns wrapped value associating with given key from this cache. If there is no entry for given key or the value is expired, a new wrapped value will be created by given loader. If the loader returns null, no value will be put and this method will return null.

        This method will return null if and only if the loader returns null.

        Parameters:
        key - given key
        loader - given loader
        Returns:
        value associating with given key from this cache, or created one
